title: 2010.09.19-MotoGP.14.Spain.Race.BBC2_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.09.19-MotoGP.14.Spain.Race.BBC2_UK-TDMK1.m4v

The Aragon Grand Prix MotoGP. Jennie Gow presents coverage of the 13th round of the season from the Ciudad del Motor de Aragon. This is the inaugural staging of the race and one in which Spanish riders Jorge Lorenzo and Dani Pedrosa are expected to continue their dominance of the championship. With commentary by Charlie Cox, Steve Parrish and Matt Roberts.

Now encoded as \'MP4 All Play\'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I\'ve made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, iPad all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
